		"description": "<p><em><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-785a9d35-7fff-a52a-7d42-6cb6d801c8ab\"><strong>Type:</strong> Shape; <strong>Level:</strong> 9</span></em></p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-4a6869a1-7fff-f06c-ff45-e4a429a1424e\">By spending 5 spell points, your blast manifests as a 10-ft radius circle cloud at a point in range, dealing half damage to any creature that enters the area or starts their turn inside it. The cloud lightly obscures the area, blocking sight. The cloud has a duration of concentration (up to 1 minute), but you must spend an action each round to maintain it. For every 1 additional spell point spent, increase the radius of the cloud by 5 ft.</span></p>",
